{"tid":1296053,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解芒亨拎盾要用右手?","createTime":"2019-07-08T08:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T14:07:59.000Z","uid":123926,"like":1690,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"c51f3741f683c6de92da72f57cfe2705af1f88b9","tid":1296053,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"芒亨就黎出新DLC就好多人都知,<br />\n一直以黎大家都有一個疑問, 點解常用手(右手)係拎盾, 非常用手(左手)反而拎武器呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2NyfQi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2NyfQi.jpg&h=208a1768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用盾御力果啲咁高技巧嘅就唔講喇<br />\n盾防嘅基本就係要盡量緊貼身體,<br />\n尤其是面對野獸兇猛嘅攻擊,<br />\n一定要側身企, 紥衡馬步, 用盡全身氣力去擋.<br />\n呢個時候如果左手拎盾嘅話,<br />\n防御時嘅衝擊力會直接傳到心臟,<br />\n嚴重時會導至休克, 甚至死亡.<br />\n所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拎盾一定要右手 <br />\n拎盾一定要右手<br />\n拎盾一定要右手</span></span></strong><br />\n重要嘅事一定要講3次<br />\n祝大家穿梳各任務都可以戰勝歸來"},{"pid":"98fec4bc927834fc4f8979fbdb81664793ed17d4","tid":1296053,"uid":272028,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:45:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8d75fbbe4aed7cc91fd935a25fc9b0bdc5ca3266","tid":1296053,"uid":123926,"like":627,"dislike":1,"score":626,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"sor! 少出post 出錯左喺政事台, 呢個應該出喺遊戲台先啱嘅"},{"pid":"f14ad360ef31b37a75a4db7c2c02e9804a3e1a85","tid":1296053,"uid":276139,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"7ddce20f21a75a3cf1ab31d94ce837bc6bf70209","tid":1296053,"uid":53687,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"長知識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed7e609c6b1497b749bd0ae25b920b9d7f8a0c7","tid":1296053,"uid":170014,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:49:18.000Z","msg":"長知識了"},{"pid":"bc69e7b5f4ac5df2a5a56b5a4fbf2ac52f5678e5","tid":1296053,"uid":261433,"like"