要右手 <br />\n拎盾一定要右手<br />\n拎盾一定要右手</span></span></strong><br />\n重要嘅事一定要講3次<br />\n祝大家穿梳各任務都可以戰勝歸來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"右手拎武器順手啲喎<br />\n對住啲小怪唔會爆心臟掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8nppofx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nppofx.png&h=eef1ce5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831ff19234adb78211a5f076af30767d05c961c8","tid":1296053,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a204f3b587a95812df499dcf1173fe84b158335a","tid":1296053,"uid":117729,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"但見NPC係用左手渣既？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"平手劍嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb9c00861bbf9d2893fd8538c9b7aed3c1e84d5","tid":1296053,"uid":263722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:59:33.000Z","msg":"我要求盾斧支援<br />\n<br />\n等D速龍打到攰一野超解炸落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51835fbe71e3d2d045ee111f79484dad5a780b3b","tid":1296053,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"831ff19234adb78211a5f076af30767d05c961c8","tid":1296053,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a204f3b587a95812df499dcf1173fe84b158335a","tid":1296053,"uid":117729,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"但見NPC係用左手渣既？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"平手劍嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply